
To load the initial database.

1) create user cdn with password charlton on MySQL.
2) Create the database "bobiles_church".
3) restore the backup contained in initial_database_load.sql
   via the mysql utility
4) create the required views by running the churchviews.sql script
   via the mysql utility.
   
Note that database connection parameters are stored in the directory
above this one in the file dbconnectparms.php.  
   
